description: Residential redevelopment. Demolition of existing 14 flats at St Joseph Court and other associated out buildings. Construction of 4 to 9 storey blocks of building to form 100 self contained flats (32 x 1 bed - 58 x 2 bed - 10 x 3 bed) and 17 x 3 to 4 bedroom houses with associated works and landscaping.
